7:13:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最刻深就係依首歌 好有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有冇喺片出現過㗎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>有出現過啦</blockquote><br />\n隔籬登有人提醒我，其實 古古惑惑 係主題曲黎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nkJhrNwsTlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnkJhrNwsTlw&d=woWKBtP6PCnvw6rWWJT%2B2v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d4d1d320\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nkJhrNwsTlw</a><br />\n2:47<br />\n<br />\n我都冇留意到吖 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/205806_43f88381302798b61261eac380058541.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F205806_43f88381302798b61261eac380058541.png&h=7108e4e3&s={SIZE}\" />，其實我最熟反而係<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lRbXYVZmTiM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlRbXYVZmTiM&d=woWKBtP6PCnvw6rWWJT%2B2v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f8c93bb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lRbXYVZmTiM</a><br />\n<br />\n但我前幾日睇另一套黑社會既片又突然諗起 古古惑惑<br />\n<br />\n咁冇野喇，原來真係主題曲黎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/205806_43f88381302798b61261eac380058541.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F205806_43f88381302798b61261eac380058541.png&h=7108e4e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e97c8fd0